name: Orangered Mage (nullchain mage)
description: In the first War of Ugoondom, it became increasingly clear the original goon mages were getting killed off, and their abilities deleted forever. Before entered battle, their abilities were cloned and minted on the Nullchain. Any Voidnull can be manifested with one of these minted mages, and the only way to destroy them completely is to destroy the Nullchain.
